<p>
[As I also] asked [your?] all-wise and admirable [friendship?] in person on account of a little radish-oil, I beseech your [all-wise?] friendship (sc. now), if it seems not too much trouble for you, two <emph rend="italics">solidi</emph> … to bring to us with you, since … we have [need?] of them. I have asked the most decent [sister] the lady Anastasia to write to you on account of this … near you on account of Theodoros the secretary … sister the lady Anastasia, master.
</p>
</div>
<div n="v" type="textpart">
